pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: post.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: seowoo-85.github.io
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  css:
    - styles.css
  toc: true
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  editor: visual
  theme:
    - cosmo
    - brand
  title: Blog
  listing:
    contents: post
    type: grid
    sort: date desc
    categories: true
